# This folder is the source for the PUBLIC GitHub profile README
# (github.com/jamesbond379), AND it hosts the private FitzJobs pipeline.
#
# To guarantee no pipeline file, resume, DB artifact, or job folder ever leaks
# into the public profile repo, we WHITELIST: ignore everything, then explicitly
# un-ignore only the profile assets.

# 1) Ignore everything by default.
*

# 2) Un-ignore the profile README and its icon assets.
!.gitignore
!README.md
!assets/
!assets/**

# (Everything else — fitz_*.py, *.bat, fitz_profile.json, bridge/, FitzJob */,
#  *.docx, *.pdf, jobs_input.json, scores*.json, run_log.txt, the venv, etc. —
#  stays out of the public profile repo.)
